<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id6c05e651-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2021—<ref href="/us/pl/117/58">Pub. L. 117–58</ref> amended section generally. Prior to amendment, section related to appropriations for fiscal years 1989 to 1994.</p>
</note>
